# Normalize line endings across every contributor's OS: store text as LF in the
# repository and check it out as LF, so CRLF never sneaks into a commit and
# diffs don't churn on the whole file when someone edits on Windows.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Generated lockfile: keep it out of code review noise (collapsed by default in
# GitHub diffs) and out of the repo's language statistics.
package-lock.json linguist-generated=true -diff

# Binary assets: never line-ending-normalized, never shown as text diffs.
*.ico binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
